              "type": "text",
              "body": "\n                                \\[\n                                \\begin{align}\n                                (x-3)^2+(y+1)^2&amp;=20\\\\\n                                (x-3)^2+(\\color{red}{x-2}+1)^2&amp;=20\\\\\n                                (x-3)^2+(x-1)^2&amp;=20\\\\\n                                (x-3)^2+(x-1)^2-20&amp;=0\n                                \\end{align}\n                                \\]\n                            "
            },
            {
